title: ETH v1 Update: Raise $OCEAN collateral cap
body:
Intro: This is a vote to raise the collateral cap of OCEAN on C.R.E.A.M. ETH v1 market.
Proposal: Listing Committee
Rational: OCEAN is currently capped out on ETH v1 market.

For:

Raise collateral cap of $OCEAN to 1,500,000 tokens or $1M USD.

Against:

Do not make any changes to ETH v1 market.
author: 0x6B1050C1C6B288C79Ac1db299Dc481048aBBBbcD
